Finance
There is a range of financial support from the government that you can access while you are unable to return due to coronavirus restrictions.
Returning to the UK
When you arrive back in the UK, follow the guidance for when you return to the UK on steps you should take to protect yourself and others.
Further information
If you need urgent consular assistance, you should contact your local British embassy, high commission or consulate. All telephones numbers are available 24/7.
